nodes.text: Ollobo was a Quarren male. Sometime after 0 BBY, he worked as a junk dealer in Jabba's Palace on Tatooine.

Ollobo appeared as a non-player character in the video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online-role playing game developed by Sony and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011.
